title: Chris Sorenson from Saosin
itunes:title: Chris Sorenson from Saosin
description:
In this episode we review new music from The Get Up Kids, Mogwai and Mother Of Mercy as well as the movie The Green Hornet. Our special guest/interview is with Chris Sorenson from the band Saosin.
